\f2\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf2 \cb3 I played a central role in shaping and implementing IOM\'92s Shelter and Settlements programming across Kenya, with strong technical contributions to the development of the National Shelter Strategy for Kenya and the integration of a multi-sectoral approach, while promoting community engagement, dialogues and fostering collaboration among ministries and counties through the national partnership coalition. Within these partnerships, I held discussions to improve migration governance, notably driving the adoption of the National Shelter Strategy. I supported in the management of shelter and settlements programme activities, ensuring projects met donor requirements, scope, budget, and timelines.\'a0\AppleTypeServices \'a0
\f0\fs24 \cb1 \

\f2\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cb3 Additionally, I provided essential coordination support to IOM\'92s leadership role in the inter-agency platforms and technical working groups, including government authorities, UN agencies, and humanitarian actors to promote harmonized climate mitigation and adaptation. I led capacity building for government and partners. Played a key role in strengthening cross-cutting themes and contributed to project development and resource mobilization efforts.\AppleTypeServices \'a0
\f0\fs24 \cb1 \

