\f2\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf2 \cb3 I led the coordination and implementation of IOM\'92s Camp Coordination and Camp Management (CCCM) programming and strategic planning with a strong focus on community participation, accountability, and service quality across displacement sites, host communities, and returnee areas. I provided strategic technical input to develop IOM\'92s camp management strategy, while overseeing daily operations of field teams and ensuring effective, inclusive governance. Under my leadership, I represented IOM in inter-agency meetings, engaging in discussions, focusing on key program priorities related to protection, gender and migration. Additionally, I played a key role in multi-sector service monitoring, gap identification, and improvement interventions. Additionally, I represented IOM in high-level cluster and inter-agency coordination platforms, advancing harmonized, protection-sensitive responses. A key achievement was piloting an information hub to facilitate CCCM support across 23 sites in Ethiopia. Additionally, I managed relationships with other UN agencies and civil society organizations focusing on migration and displacement issues.\AppleTypeServices \'a0
